#. Tag: sect2
#: contexthelp.docbook:1
#, no-c-format
msgid "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"
msgstr "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many functions and views have help and hints that can be displayed with the "
"<emphasis>What's This</emphasis> function."
msgstr ""
"Številne funkcije in pogledi imajo pomoč in namige, ki jih je mogoče "
"prikazati s funkcijo <emphasis>Kaj je to</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate it with the menu entry <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>WhatsThis</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or keyboard "
"shortcut <keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Aktivirate ga lahko z menijskim vnosom <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>KajJeTo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico na "
"tipkovnici <keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo >."

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In dialogs it is activated by pressing the <varname>?</varname> in the "
"dialogs title bar."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornih oknih se aktivira s pritiskom <varname>?</varname> v naslovni "
"vrstici pogovornega okna."
